Not any fault of Amazon, but the season suck!

They're all there, the last season of the Brady Bunch, uncut and no commercials.  Video quality is very good, and the packaging is good, very compact.  If you tuned in mainly to watch Marcia, this was her year; what teenage boy in America wasn't in love with her?  But it's probably good that they stopped production after five seasons.  Greg would have moved on to college, breaking up the set of 3 girls vs. 3 boys.  It might not have worked.
I grew up with Brady Bunch, loved the series.
